  "instructions": [
    "In a large molcajete, combine olive oil, miso paste, garlic, lemon juice, paprika, black pepper, and crushed red pepper. ",
    "Mix until a smooth paste forms.",
    "Add the gigantes beans and seafood stock to the molcajete and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Stir in the chopped parsley and dill.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a baking dish and top with gluten-free breadcrumbs, if using.",
    "Bake at 375°F (190°C) for 20 minutes, or until the top is golden brown and the gigantes are heated through."
  ],
